IC.Types
Class TypeTable

java.lang.Object
  IC.Types.TypeTable

public class TypeTable
extends java.lang.Object

This class is in charge on creating the Type Table The Type table hold all the types that the running program uses When traveling over the AST every Type that we encounter enters to the this table Also when a Symbol requests its type its getting it from this table.
